        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3320902520" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8284763007651746167"><strong>Tha last book of the trilogy</strong><br/><br/>I read the first two books in this trilogy in order. The first captivated me and I couldn&apos;t wait to read the second. I found that book slightly less enthralling but nonetheless enjoyed the journey. Book three I found a little more difficult. It seemed to bog down in places and I found my attention wandering. However, it was good to have the series fully resolved in the end and I&apos;m pleased that I persevered. </span>
  <span id="freeText8284763007651746167" style="display:none"><strong>Tha last book of the trilogy</strong><br /><br />I read the first two books in this trilogy in order. The first captivated me and I couldn't wait to read the second. I found that book slightly less enthralling but nonetheless enjoyed the journey. Book three I found a little more difficult. It seemed to bog down in places and I found my attention wandering. However, it was good to have the series fully resolved in the end and I'm pleased that I persevered. </span>
